<li><a href="http://track.spe.schoolmessenger.com/f/a/Nx1_hnnTPVvuF4Hpg_iGBg~~/AAAAAQA~/RgRgcMipP0SBaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cueW91dHViZS5jb20vd2F0Y2g_dj1QcmFYLXFsY0pxUSZmZWF0dXJlPXlvdXR1LmJlJmZiY2xpZD1Jd0FSMWVjZFlVZW8tTWZyTzVjSWlpSlBvQmFfQzlKcGxEZEFmX1U4TktHUnJTNTd3QUxqQVhmaERydUkwVwdzY2hvb2xtQgoAACmVj17PVxF6UhFuc3ltb25kc0BkMTIzLm9yZ1gEAAAAAQ~~" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" data-saferedirecturl="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://track.spe.schoolmessenger.com/f/a/Nx1_hnnTPVvuF4Hpg_iGBg~~/AAAAAQA~/RgRgcMipP0SBaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cueW91dHViZS5jb20vd2F0Y2g_dj1QcmFYLXFsY0pxUSZmZWF0dXJlPXlvdXR1LmJlJmZiY2xpZD1Jd0FSMWVjZFlVZW8tTWZyTzVjSWlpSlBvQmFfQzlKcGxEZEFmX1U4TktHUnJTNTd3QUxqQVhmaERydUkwVwdzY2hvb2xtQgoAACmVj17PVxF6UhFuc3ltb25kc0BkMTIzLm9yZ1gEAAAAAQ~~&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1586955173167000&amp;usg=AFQjCNG0oyL3vMez2vpMrqMa3Rv80Ch_4Q">Kolmar – We Miss You</a></li>
<li><a href="http://track.spe.schoolmessenger.com/f/a/G3SblyeK-nEh75jNS8EZdw~~/AAAAAQA~/RgRgcMipP0RGaHR0cHM6Ly9kcml2ZS5nb29nbGUuY29tL2ZpbGUvZC8xYVRmd0RQS19LNTZ4WkY5ZEUtSWRMMnpOZEI5TVplaEkvdmlld1cHc2Nob29sbUIKAAAplY9ez1cRelIRbnN5bW9uZHNAZDEyMy5vcmdYBAAAAAE~" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" data-saferedirecturl="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://track.spe.schoolmessenger.com/f/a/G3SblyeK-nEh75jNS8EZdw~~/AAAAAQA~/RgRgcMipP0RGaHR0cHM6Ly9kcml2ZS5nb29nbGUuY29tL2ZpbGUvZC8xYVRmd0RQS19LNTZ4WkY5ZEUtSWRMMnpOZEI5TVplaEkvdmlld1cHc2Nob29sbUIKAAAplY9ez1cRelIRbnN5bW9uZHNAZDEyMy5vcmdYBAAAAAE~&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1586955173167000&amp;usg=AFQjCNHMEDnzyAQOlvX-Q895LeDnGU6qWw">Sward – We Miss You</a></li>
<li><a href="http://track.spe.schoolmessenger.com/f/a/3czqTiZAVDdTdxeBkHyxWA~~/AAAAAQA~/RgRgcMipP0Q8aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cueW91dHViZS5jb20vd2F0Y2g_dj1IS2FmYUk5ZmozdyZmZWF0dXJlPXlvdXR1LmJlVwdzY2hvb2xtQgoAACmVj17PVxF6UhFuc3ltb25kc0BkMTIzLm9yZ1gEAAAAAQ~~" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" data-saferedirecturl="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://track.spe.schoolmessenger.com/f/a/3czqTiZAVDdTdxeBkHyxWA~~/AAAAAQA~/RgRgcMipP0Q8aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cueW91dHViZS5jb20vd2F0Y2g_dj1IS2FmYUk5ZmozdyZmZWF0dXJlPXlvdXR1LmJlVwdzY2hvb2xtQgoAACmVj17PVxF6UhFuc3ltb25kc0BkMTIzLm9yZ1gEAAAAAQ~~&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1586955173167000&amp;usg=AFQjCNE-eQI2T7INTSN4MrmS9e83ZphvjA">OLHMS Message for Students</a></li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<p>As a reminder, Grab &amp; Go Meal pickup will not be available on Friday, April 10 or Monday, April 13. Families should have received extra meals today during meal pickup.</p>
<p>As we move further into our new Remote Learning reality, it is my sincere privilege to share <a href="http://track.spe.schoolmessenger.com/f/a/Vu2POQknO7v37cRlqtMJSw~~/AAAAAQA~/RgRgcMipP0RXaHR0cHM6Ly9kb2NzLmdvb2dsZS5jb20vZG9jdW1lbnQvZC8xWkhPblVGSDVOMmViMi1JdExzaWF1VGJHRTNlWlNwNC1UWTJJdEpFaGhKNC9wcmV2aWV3VwdzY2hvb2xtQgoAACmVj17PVxF6UhFuc3ltb25kc0BkMTIzLm9yZ1gEAAAAAQ~~" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" data-saferedirecturl="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://track.spe.schoolmessenger.com/f/a/Vu2POQknO7v37cRlqtMJSw~~/AAAAAQA~/RgRgcMipP0RXaHR0cHM6Ly9kb2NzLmdvb2dsZS5jb20vZG9jdW1lbnQvZC8xWkhPblVGSDVOMmViMi1JdExzaWF1VGJHRTNlWlNwNC1UWTJJdEpFaGhKNC9wcmV2aWV3VwdzY2hvb2xtQgoAACmVj17PVxF6UhFuc3ltb25kc0BkMTIzLm9yZ1gEAAAAAQ~~&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1586955173167000&amp;usg=AFQjCNGmFBileRnScUCiODZkEdix4KzANQ">D123’s Remote Learning Guidance Document</a> with you. This plan was created as a collaborative effort between District 123 administration, teachers, families, and our union partners in an attempt to merge <a href="http://track.spe.schoolmessenger.com/f/a/1RZwG-0kGytmlJG8OAYuDA~~/AAAAAQA~/RgRgcMipP0Q9aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuaXNiZS5uZXQvRG9jdW1lbnRzL1JMLVJlY29tbWVuZGF0aW9ucy0zLTI3LTIwLnBkZlcHc2Nob29sbUIKAAAplY9ez1cRelIRbnN5bW9uZHNAZDEyMy5vcmdYBAAAAAE~" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" data-saferedirecturl="https://www.google.com/url?q=http://track.spe.schoolmessenger.com/f/a/1RZwG-0kGytmlJG8OAYuDA~~/AAAAAQA~/RgRgcMipP0Q9aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuaXNiZS5uZXQvRG9jdW1lbnRzL1JMLVJlY29tbWVuZGF0aW9ucy0zLTI3LTIwLnBkZlcHc2Nob29sbUIKAAAplY9ez1cRelIRbnN5bW9uZHNAZDEyMy5vcmdYBAAAAAE~&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1586955173167000&amp;usg=AFQjCNHRyMNHvL3In7p-Y9YSwFrZVrG1yw">ISBE’s Remote Learning guidance</a> with our district’s core principles and beliefs. The plan was informed by input and feedback from various advisory committees and community surveys that engaged countless District 123 families, students, and staff members.</p>
<p>I remain steadfast in our belief that when we emerge from this public health crisis we will become a stronger and more connected District 123 learning community. I wish everyone a safe and healthy upcoming weekend. We are all in this together and we will get through this together; our unity and compassion as educators, families and community members is fundamental to our continued success.</p>
<p>Sincerely,</p>
<p>Paul J. Enderle<br>
Superintendent</p>
